<br>
&quot;Explain to me, how is a mage for example, going to kill a rogue - without the ability to kite you with his pet? you can kill him in close to one backstab, or in a few attack rounds, he cant channel spells through dual wield, and all his spells only does 66percent of their damage against you, not counting your ressists.  No thats right, he cant.&quot;<br>
<br>
You can't channel scars of sigil a 2 second spell? /boggle<br>
<br>
A kill with one double backstab doesn't occur till lvl 59 with duelist disc and even so... if you see a rogue go duelist BACKUP for the 9 seconds till it wears off!<br>
<br>
